<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, viewport-fit=cover" />
  <meta name="theme-color" content="#07070a" />
  <title>AirCanvas — Draw With Light</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Bebas+Neue&family=Manrope:wght@300;400;600;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body class="home-body">
  <div class="film-grain"></div>
  <div class="vignette"></div>

  <nav class="navbar">
    <div class="brand">AIR<span>CANVAS</span></div>
  </nav>

  <main class="hero">
    <p class="kicker">GESTURE-DRIVEN CREATIVITY</p>
    <h1>Paint the <span class="glow">air</span>.<br>Leave nothing but <span class="glow-amber">light</span>.</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">
      No brush. No mouse. Just your hand, your camera, and a canvas
      that listens. Powered by real-time hand tracking, rendered
      live in your browser.
    </p>
    <a href="/canvas" class="cta-button">
      <span>Launch Air Canvas</span>
      <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M5 12h14M13 5l7 7-7 7" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
    </a>
    <div class="hint">Requires camera access · Works best in Chrome / Edge</div>
  </main>

  <footer class="footer">Built with Express · EJS · MediaPipe Hands</footer>
</body>
</html>
